metadata.name: still in a state of bewildermen
metadata.description:
he saw a heavy arrow coming at him with murderous force.



She knows Cang Qiao can hide, he is the first master of the inner court.



Can be...



He closed his eyes coldly and calmly let the arrow Pierce his throat.



Cang Qiao's hot blood scattered on her corpse face that moment, she could feel his blood scalding sweet.



The heat made her soul tremble.



And then...
